net.java.jddac.common.meas
Class Measurement

java.lang.Object
  net.java.jddac.common.type.ArgArray
      net.java.jddac.common.meas.Measurement

public class Measurement
extends ArgArray

This class represents a physical observation. It is typically created by a channel in a BasicTIM FunctionBlock. While its current form is simply an extension of ArgArray, xml generation and other serialization needs require us to be able to distinguish between a Measurement and an ArgArray. The names for the attributes should be taken from MeasAttr whenever possible.
